data.name: label16.Text
data.value: - You can protect a branch to avoid accidental actions. - You won't be able to access a protected branch. To edit themes in a protected branch, either unprotect it or clone it as an unprotected branch if you want to keep a protected instance.

data.name: label15.Text
data.value: - PRs must be approved by Abdelrhman-AK before they can be merged. - You may continue modifying your PR as long as it has not yet been approved. - Commit additional changes to the same branch to update the PR. - When approved, delete the branch (don't use it again). Always create a fresh branch for each new theme upload session.

data.name: label10.Text
data.value: - Before you begin, create a new branch specifically for your theme work. - Example branch name: theme/my-new-theme. - The 'main' branch will not be listed here, as it is protected for syncing purposes.
